  "The zero vector (0,0,0) satisfies 0+0+0=0. If x1+y1+z1=0 and x2+y2+z2=0, then (x1+x2)+(y1+y2)+(z1+z2)=0, so closed under addition. If x+y+z=0, then cx+cy+cz=c(x+y+z)=0, so closed under scalar multiplication.": "",
  "Which of the following subsets of R^2 is NOT a subspace?": "",
