  "A climate scientist stores monthly temperature anomaly data as vectors in R^12 (one component per month). She considers the subset where the sum of all 12 components equals zero (meaning no net annual anomaly). Is this a subspace of R^12?": "",
  "Only if the anomalies are measured in Celsius": "",
