  "A network engineer represents data packets as vectors in R^4 where the components are (source IP hash, destination IP hash, packet size, timestamp offset). She considers the subset of packets where the source and destination hashes are equal (i.e., loopback packets of the form (a, a, b, c)). Is this a subspace of R^4?": "",
